com.knitting.jamacoi
Class Rectangular_CVS_Matrix

java.lang.Object
  com.knitting.jamacoi.Rectangular_CVS_Matrix

public class Rectangular_CVS_Matrix
extends java.lang.Object

This class provides the ability to read in a rectangular matrix from a disk file which can then be used as input to the Regression class.

The rectangular matrix must contain the same number of fields on each line. Each field on a line must be separated from its neighboring field by a comma. Hence the CVS string in the class name.

Hint: after the comma field-separater, spaces can be used before the next field's digits start. This allows the data be vertically aligned to aid in human review of the file's contents.
